   Legal Documents and Regulations
     * Board Governance Memorandum
       This August 30, 1999 memorandum was prepared by the CSBs Office of
       General Counsel. The memorandum explains the CSBs enabling statute
       and describes the functions and responsibilities of the Chairman,
       the Board Members, and the Board as a whole.
